# Card-compatibility puzzle: Prodigal Sorcerer ("Tim", LEA-class 1/1 pinger).
#
# Aspects exercised:
#   * Activated ability with a tap cost (AB$ DealDamage | Cost$ T) — CR 602.1.
#   * The ability taps the Sorcerer as its cost.
#   * "any target" targeting (ValidTgts$ Any), NumDmg$ 1: deals exactly 1 damage.
#   * 1 damage is lethal to a 1/1 (Mons's Goblin Raiders), which dies to the
#     lethal-damage state-based action (CR 704.5g).
#   * No summoning sickness: the Sorcerer was already in play at puzzle start,
#     so it may activate a {T} ability the turn the puzzle begins.
#
# Scenario: P0 controls Prodigal Sorcerer + two Islands; the opponent has a 1/1
# Mons's Goblin Raiders. The heuristic AI taps the Sorcerer to ping the Raiders,
# killing it; later the Sorcerer (now an unblocked 1/1) attacks for 1.
# Verified live (seed 42):
#   "Prodigal Sorcerer activates ability ... deals 1 damage to any target"
#   "Mons's Goblin Raiders takes 1 damage ... dies from lethal damage"
#
# Reproduce:
#   mtg tui --start-state test_puzzles/prodigal_sorcerer_ping.pzl \
#       --p1 heuristic --p2 heuristic --seed 42 -v 2 --no-color-logs

[metadata]
Name:Prodigal Sorcerer — {T}: 1 damage pings a 1/1 dead
Goal:Win
Turns:3
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0's Prodigal Sorcerer uses its {T} ability to deal 1 damage to the opponent's 1/1 Mons's Goblin Raiders, which is lethal and the creature dies. Exercises the tap-cost activated ability, any-target NumDmg$ 1, and the lethal-damage state-based action.

[state]
turn=3
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=
p0library=Island;Island;Island;Island;Island
p0graveyard=
p0battlefield=Island;Island;Prodigal Sorcerer
p0exile=

p1life=20
p1hand=
p1library=Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest
p1graveyard=
p1battlefield=Mons's Goblin Raiders
p1exile=

[assertions]
# The {T}-cost ability resolved and its 1 damage was lethal to the 1/1.
creature died Mons's Goblin Raiders
# The pinged creature ended up in the opponent's graveyard.
opponent graveyard contains Mons's Goblin Raiders
# P0 took no damage doing this.
life eq 20
